<p><font color=#669900><b>K3b -- the DIY Tool for Creating CDs</b></font></p>

<p>Copy and create audio, data, and mixed-mode CDs with K3b, the
KDE CD burning application. Following the installation, use K3b to
create a new backup project -- protect yourself against
loss of data.</p>

<p><b>Added Value</b></p>
<p>If you own a DVD burner, K3b can use it as a burning device as well. Furthermore,
you can easily burn CD images from your harddisk to a CD.</p>
